javafxapplicationud3example.ui.controller

Class HelpController

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafxapplicationud3example.ui.controller.HelpController

  • public class HelpController
extends java.lang.Object
    Controller class for help window . It shows a help page that explains how to use the user's data management window. The view is defined in Help.fmxl file and the help page is help.html.
